sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant AGServer as autogluonserver<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (plaintext)
    participant Factory as predictor_factory.py<br/>Auto-Detection
    participant Tabular as AutoGluonTabularModel<br/>v1 + v2 Protocol
    participant TimeSeries as AutoGluonTimeSeriesModel<br/>v1 Protocol
    participant Storage as kserve-storage<br/>S3/GCS/Azure/HF
    participant CloudStore as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over AGServer,CloudStore: Flow 1: Model Load at Startup

    AGServer->>AGServer: runtime_paths.py<br/>Relocate CWD to writable dir
    AGServer->>Factory: Create AutoGluonDetectedModel
    Factory->>Factory: version_compat.py<br/>Patch-level tolerance check
    Factory->>Storage: Download model from storageUri
    Storage->>CloudStore: HTTPS/443<br/>IAM/SA/Token Auth
    CloudStore-->>Storage: Model Artifacts
    Storage-->>Factory: Model files on local filesystem
    alt TimeSeriesPredictor detected
        Factory->>TimeSeries: Load as TimeSeriesPredictor
        TimeSeries-->>Factory: Model ready
    else TabularPredictor detected
        Factory->>Tabular: Load as TabularPredictor
        Tabular-->>Factory: Model ready
    end
    Factory-->>AGServer: Model registered with ModelServer

    Note over Client,Tabular: Flow 2: Tabular Inference (v1 REST)

    Client->>KRBP: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    KRBP->>KRBP: Authenticate & Authorize
    KRBP->>AGServer: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost, plaintext)
    AGServer->>Tabular: predict(instances)
    Tabular->>Tabular: TabularPredictor.predict()<br/>or predict_proba() if PREDICT_PROBA=true
    Tabular-->>AGServer: Predictions JSON
    AGServer-->>KRBP: 200 OK + JSON Response
    KRBP-->>Client: HTTPS Response<br/>TLS 1.3

    Note over Client,Tabular: Flow 2b: Tabular Inference (v2 REST)

    Client->>KRBP: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    KRBP->>AGServer: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    AGServer->>Tabular: predict(InferRequest)
    Tabular->>Tabular: Parse tensors per feature<br/>(INT64, FP64, BOOL, BYTES)
    Tabular-->>AGServer: InferResponse (tensors)
    AGServer-->>KRBP: 200 OK + InferResponse
    KRBP-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,TimeSeries: Flow 3: Time Series Forecast (v1 REST)

    Client->>KRBP: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    KRBP->>AGServer: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    AGServer->>TimeSeries: predict(instances, known_covariates)
    TimeSeries->>TimeSeries: TimeSeriesPredictor.predict()
    TimeSeries-->>AGServer: Forecast JSON
    AGServer-->>KRBP: 200 OK + JSON Response
    KRBP-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over AGServer,AGServer: Health & Metrics

    Note right of AGServer: GET /v2/health/ready → Readiness probe<br/>GET /v2/health/live → Liveness probe<br/>GET /metrics → Prometheus metrics
